text: Ibitiruna araponga is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 1997. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Ibitiruna araponga. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1997
title: Ibitiruna araponga
